h3cMinm.name: h3cMinm

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB.

h3cMinm.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085

H3cMinmEnabledStatus.name: H3cMinmEnabledStatus
H3cMinmEnabledStatus.description: A enumerated value which indicates the state of object.

h3cMinmCapabilities.name: h3cMinmCapabilities
h3cMinmCapabilities.description: This object displays the MAC-in-MAC capabilities with respect to certain fields. The following values may be supported: reEncapsulation: Support for configuring re-encapsulation (denoted by h3cMinmVsiReEncapsulation). uplink: Support for configuring uplink (denoted by h3cMinmUplinkTable). vsiShareConnection: It indicates that connection entry is shared in all VSIs. h3cVsiIndex is meaningless and must be value 1 in h3cMinmConnectionTable.

h3cMinmBmac.name: h3cMinmBmac
h3cMinmBmac.description: A MAC address used in creating the MAC header of I-tagged frames transmitted across a Provider Backbone Bridged Network. The invalid value FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF indicates that this node is not supported by the device.

h3cMinmVsiTable.name: h3cMinmVsiTable
h3cMinmVsiTable.description: A table for configuring MAC-in-MAC service instance parameter.

h3cMinmVsiEntry.name: h3cMinmVsiEntry
h3cMinmVsiEntry.description: An entry for configuring MAC-in-MAC service instance parameter.

h3cMinmVsiBvlan.name: h3cMinmVsiBvlan
h3cMinmVsiBvlan.description: BVLAN ID. The value 65535 indicates the BVLAN has not been configured for get operation, and it indicates deleting the BVLAN configration for set operation.

h3cMinmVsiReEncapsulation.name: h3cMinmVsiReEncapsulation
h3cMinmVsiReEncapsulation.description: Whether the re-encapsulation is enabled. The reEncapsulation field of h3cMinmCapabilities denotes whether this node is supported.

h3cMinmVsiNextAvailableLinkId.name: h3cMinmVsiNextAvailableLinkId
h3cMinmVsiNextAvailableLinkId.description: Next available connection entry index for creating a connection entry. Its value ranges from 0x1 to 0xFFFFFFFF.The invalid value 0xFFFFFFFF indicates that connection entry can not be created. When the vsiShareConnection field of h3cMinmCapabilities is set, this node returns an invalid value if the value of h3cVsiIndex is not 1.

h3cMinmUplinkTable.name: h3cMinmUplinkTable
h3cMinmUplinkTable.description: A table for uplink ports of the VSI in MAC-in-MAC. The uplink field of h3cMinmCapabilities denotes whether this table is supported.

h3cMinmUplinkEntry.name: h3cMinmUplinkEntry
h3cMinmUplinkEntry.description: An entry for uplink ports of the VSI in MAC-in-MAC.

h3cMinmUplinkRowStatus.name: h3cMinmUplinkRowStatus
h3cMinmUplinkRowStatus.description: Operation status of this table entry.

h3cMinmConnectionTable.name: h3cMinmConnectionTable
h3cMinmConnectionTable.description: A table for the connection information of BMAC.

h3cMinmConnectionEntry.name: h3cMinmConnectionEntry
h3cMinmConnectionEntry.description: An entry for the connection information of BMAC. When the vsiShareConnection field of h3cMinmCapabilities is set, connection entry is shared in all VSIs. h3cVsiIndex is meaningless and must be value 1 in h3cMinmConnectionTable.

h3cMinmConnectionLinkId.name: h3cMinmConnectionLinkId
h3cMinmConnectionLinkId.description: Entry index when the vsiShareConnection bit of h3cMinmCapabilities is set(h3cVsiIndex is meaningless and must be value 1), else entry index in the VSI of h3cVsiIndex.Its value ranges from 0x1 to 0xFFFFFFFE. It should be obtained from h3cMinmVsiNextAvailableLinkId for create operation.

h3cMinmConnectionPort.name: h3cMinmConnectionPort
h3cMinmConnectionPort.description: Port ifindex of an connection entry.

h3cMinmConnectionAgingStatus.name: h3cMinmConnectionAgingStatus
h3cMinmConnectionAgingStatus.description: Aging time of an connection entry.

h3cMinmConnectionRowStatus.name: h3cMinmConnectionRowStatus
h3cMinmConnectionRowStatus.description: Operation status of this table entry.
